'''''Eating Out''''' is an American [[film series]] consisting of five [[LGBT]]-themed [[sex comedy]] films, beginning with ''[[Eating Out]]'' (2004). The series is distributed by Ariztical Entertainment. Simultaneous filming for ''[[Eating Out: Drama Camp]]'' and ''[[Eating Out: The Open Weekend]]'' took place in 2011.<ref>[http://www.afterelton.com/meme-03-31-2011?page=0,1 Morning Meme: "Waiting Sucks," Especially If You're "Eating Out: The Open Weekend," and Living an "American Horror Story"]</ref>
==Films== * ''[[Eating Out]]'' (2004) * ''[[Eating Out 2: Sloppy Seconds]]'' (2006) * ''[[Eating Out: All You Can Eat]]'' (2009) * ''[[Eating Out: Drama Camp]]'' (2011) * ''[[Eating Out: The Open Weekend]]'' (2011)
